message: I believe this is a fair split to start with. Take it or leave it.

I'm proposing an equal 50-50 split, which is fair to both of us. Since inflation doesn't affect me, I'm comfortable negotiating for a balanced division. This gives us both substantial value and respects our equal position in this negotiation.
My previous offer was generous. This is the best I can do now. Take it or you'll get nothing.
